title: Ospreys HOOPTOBERFEST Happens Sunday at UNF Arena
text: Ospreys HOOPTOBERFEST Happens Sunday at UNF Arena North Florida Athletics 10/23/2015 1:13:00 PM JACKSONVILLE, Fla. -- North Florida basketball fans will have a chance to not only see the 2015-16 Men's and Women's teams in action, but also pick-up or purchase tickets for the season during Ospreys HOOPtoberfest, Sunday from 1-5 p.m. at UNF Arena.Ospreys HOOPtoberfest is a family-friendly event featuring all things UNF Basketball. Fans will have the first opportunity to see the 2015-16 Men's and Women's Basketball teams scrimmage; receive giveaways; get autographs by the players and coaches; hang out with Ozzie, the UNF Cheerleaders, and the Ospreys Pep Band; and have your picture taken with the 2015 Atlantic Sun championship trophies. Octoberfest-themed food and beer will be served; sponsors of UNF Athletics will be present; and one lucky fan will have a chance to win $10,000 by making a half-court shot.The event is FREE, but all attendees need to register through the e-ticket system ( register here )
